    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200\u00b0C/ 180\u00b0C (fan)/ 425\u00b0F/ Gas 7</p> <p>Chop the <strong>sweet potato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> (skins on) into small, bite-sized pieces</p> <p>Trim the green stalks off the <strong>aubergine<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and chop into bite-sized pieces</p> <p>Deseed the <strong>red pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-fish-rainbow-veg-and-chilli-yoghurt/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped vegetables</strong> to a baking tray with 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[5 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong></p> <p>Add the <strong>cumin seeds</strong>\u00a0with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong>\u00a0</strong>give everything a good mix up\u00a0</p> <p>Put the tray in the oven for 15-20 min or until everything is cooked through\u00a0</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-fish-rainbow-veg-and-chilli-yoghurt/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice the <strong>spring onions</strong> finely</p> <p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p> <p>\u00a0</p> <p>\u00a0</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-fish-rainbow-veg-and-chilli-yoghurt/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Pat the <strong>basa fillets</strong> dry with <strong>kitchen paper</strong></p> <p>Add 3 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tsp]</span><strong> flour</strong> to a plate with the <strong>ground cumin</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p> <p>Give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>flour mixture</strong></p> <p>\u00a0</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-fish-rainbow-veg-and-chilli-yoghurt/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>basa fillets</strong> to the plate and press them into the <strong>flour mixture</strong> until fully coated</p> <p>\u00a0</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-fish-rainbow-veg-and-chilli-yoghurt/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong>\u00a0over a high heat</p> <p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated basa fillets</strong>, reduce\u00a0the heat to medium and cook for 2 min on each side or until cooked through and lightly crisp \u2013 this is your<strong> crispy fried fish</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-fish-rainbow-veg-and-chilli-yoghurt/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine\u00a0the <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and <strong>Sriracha</strong>\u00a0(Can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a small bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt\u00a0</strong>\u2013 this is your\u00a0<strong>chilli yoghurt</strong></p> <p>Once cooked, mix\u00a0the<strong> vegetables </strong>with the<strong> chopped spring onion </strong>and <strong>half</strong> of the<strong> chopped coriander </strong><span class=\"text-highlight\">\u2013 these are your<strong> roasted vegetables\u00a0</strong></span></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-fish-rainbow-veg-and-chilli-yoghurt/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy</strong>\u00a0<strong>fried fish</strong>\u00a0over the <strong>roasted vegetables</strong></p> <p>Drizzle over\u00a0the <strong>chilli yoghurt</strong> and garnish with the <strong>remaining coriander</strong></p> <p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
